{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "舊舞步", "storyInfo": "雕像燃燒的廣場上，過去與現在的舞約重疊，愛布拉娜與拉芙希妮隔著已逝的英雄對峙。一切結束後，拉芙希妮受到託付，帶著逝者離開納斯爾紗，前往遺跡。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read2"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_weaamonologue_2", "channel": "read2", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>高傲的紅龍沒有朋友，只會偶爾和鏡子裡的自己聊聊天。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>某年夏末節，她要舉辦一場盛大的宴會，需要鏡中人出來幫忙，但她們兩個不能同時出現在別人面前，否則鏡中人就會消失。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>鏡中人不得不遵循紅龍的命令，出發去邀請神秘的守靈人。守靈人卻無論如何也不願赴宴，還勸鏡中人不要再回去。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>但鏡中人仍然隻身回到紅龍的巢穴。此時宴會已經開始，鏡中人連忙躲進篝火外的黑暗。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>不知不覺中，來赴宴的人一個個消失，而紅龍硬是把鏡中人從黑暗中拉出來，強迫她和自己跳舞。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>她們跳啊跳，跳啊跳，鏡中人覺得自己的腳趾都快掉了，她想休息一下，紅龍卻無論如何也不肯停下來。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "read2"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "char", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read2", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你，拉芙希妮。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要的書，蒸汽騎士冒險故事的續集。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問我，“為什麼”？"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不需要理由，我親愛的妹妹。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，你真的需要讀這個嗎？"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讀一本要不是迫於同齡人的壓力，你其實根本就不感興趣的書？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "type": "char", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我自己想看的。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#22$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是對父親說過的嗎？你不想被其他人問為什麼會有維多利亞人不喜歡看蒸汽騎士的故事。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本書……是爸爸讓你幫我買的嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會呢。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#8$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你……為什麼會知道？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#8$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在後退，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不喜歡你像其他人一樣畏懼我。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你這麼害怕被我知道這些事情，不如來跟我跳一支舞，緩解一下緊張，如何？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的是……跳舞嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#13$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不可以是呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#8$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說著，愛布拉娜甚至優雅地朝妹妹伸出手。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在拉芙希妮的印象裡，即便在父母放起一家人都喜歡的音樂，父親搖頭晃腦，母親用手指在桌上敲著節拍的時候……"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐都只是冷冷地笑著，端坐在原位。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從未跟著音樂舞動過身體。一次都沒有。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你能跟上我的腳步時，你就不必再為一本書、一個請求或是幾個同齡的朋友煩憂了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#25$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#25$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒拆封的騎士小說掉在地上，新書好聞的氣味被泥水掩沒。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還太小，她沒想過如願以償也能如此沉重苦澀，她只記得自己踉蹌著轉身離開，沒有握住那隻伸向自己的……"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柔軟而冰冷的手。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群已經散去，不必再隱藏自己的身分了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你仍然覺得他們還活著嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道，每個塔拉人心中都燃燒著這樣的火。從我們的祖先向維多利亞人俯首開始，火就從未熄滅過。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡的人如此，那些隨我回來的人們也是一樣，只是他們的火從未染上死亡的顏色。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯的比喻，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我現在再來問問你吧，你要怎麼辦呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再去把那團火漆成你的顏色？我想你一定已經試過了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是誰，一旦沾染了死亡，你的火焰就只能將其化為灰燼。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，拉芙希妮，殺死我。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時殺死城裡的所有人？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的這麼在意一件事會如何被記述，你也可以說，是我殺了他們，你只是把他們埋葬了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "納斯爾紗的人們還活著。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕驅動那具身體的已經只剩死亡，而非生命？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果真的連一點生命的火種都不存在，他們早就變成你那些遊蕩、無知無識的行屍了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們早晚會的。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，他們不會。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寧願將活人身上的紫火視為一場瘟疫，一場因你而起的瘟疫。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你要去幫這場瘟疫尋找解藥了嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$2"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望那個解藥能讓你也一併痊癒，愛布拉娜。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真……好？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，真好，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己還沒注意到嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經在想如何治癒我，而不是如何逃避我了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來跳舞吧，拉芙希妮。跳那支我一直想邀你一起，你卻總是逃開的舞。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說……什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，來跳舞吧，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最後一個小節之前，用你的槍貫穿我的心臟。致死的瘟疫沒有解藥，你的意志足夠堅定，你的行動卻終將只是徒勞。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，別再逃避宿命了……納斯爾紗的，還有我們的。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夏末節還沒到，但生與死之間的界限已經比塔拉歷史上的任何時刻都要模糊。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的想讓塔拉變成死的國度嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮下意識地轉過頭去。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熾烈的紫火仍在英雄一路拖行至此的骨架上熊熊燃燒，而剛剛被紫火佔據、猛地站起的庫林的身體，此刻也跪倒在地。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不忍再看，於是回過頭，直視姐姐的雙眼，和那隻時隔多年重新伸向自己的手。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知是錯覺，還是紫火籠罩下的一切都會失去生機，相比記憶之中，她眼前那隻手蒼白得毫無血色。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一座城市，這是無數人的生命。愛布拉娜，這不是能用宿命兩個字輕飄飄地概括的東西。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說完了嗎？我覺得我們已經在各自的頻道講得夠久了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……愛布拉娜！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你大可以繼續長篇大論下去，反正只要你想，我就會站在這裡等你。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是快點，拉芙希妮。你終究是等得起的，其他人卻未必。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深呼吸）你說得對，你終究是等得起的，但其他人卻未必。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，這場舞我陪你跳，直到我們之中有一個倒地不起為止。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不會按你的舞步來。絕不。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悉聽尊便。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是有一件事你會錯意了，親愛的拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個等不起的人，此刻就站在你面前呢。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等不起？"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮緊緊盯著姐姐的臉龐，她突然意識到一件徹頭徹尾離題的事情。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那隻手的蒼白並非錯覺。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紫火幾乎編織成一張鋪天蓋地的披風，讓愛布拉娜顯得美麗而可怖，卻也無法掩飾她皮膚裡透出的，如同消耗性的惡疾作祟一樣的慘白。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不該是這樣的，她從沒像這樣過。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜，你……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你……還好嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜臉上泛起笑意。她的笑總掛在她的臉上，冷冰冰的。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻的笑容彷彿有了些許溫度，卻更顯得慘白的臉怵目驚心。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝關心，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這些冷漠的別離與苦楚的團聚之後，能聽見你的問候，也真的是……久違了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$2"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順便，我倒也確實想和你跳一場舞，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等我找到治好你的方法，我會和你跳的。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，我會在這裡等著的。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_marblefootsteps_loop", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "awalk"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "awalk", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜信步走向堡壘，那腳步聲飄渺到虛弱。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……紅龍！涅梅絲！", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我到城門的時候，那裡一個人都沒有！我知道一定是出了什麼事，廣場上到底——", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍，這……是？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮懷中抱著一個小小的匣子。在夜間昏暗的燈光下，似乎什麼都比平日更加模糊。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我救不了庫林，只能……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只能以這種方式讓他得以安息，不必繼續在廣場上受死火的煎熬。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊牧人沉默了半晌，在地上摸索到一枚石頭。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她用盡渾身的力氣，將那枚石頭狠狠砸向堡壘的方向。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那石頭旋即被夜裡的黑暗吞沒，甚至沒有發出一絲聲響。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宵禁已經開始了。涅梅絲、布莉吉，我們先——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲伸手從木匣上方虛虛拂過，似乎試圖擦去一些不存在的灰塵。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她忽然想起幾天前，自己被原本的同族拒絕時，那人對自己說的一些多餘的話。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守靈人不和生者團結，也不需要生者的尊重，除非他們已經死去。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才是深池理當尊重的傳統。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，多謝您還願意給我這枚哨笛……我回去了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，涅梅絲。你明知道夏末節將至，守靈人不太可能拿得出什麼祭器，但你還是來了。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些深池強迫你來的？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是我自己——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲，你的個性還真是一點都沒變。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等待、斡旋、調和……你在納斯爾紗，在那條紅龍的麾下，也執著於這樣嗎？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是……不希望看到本該向好的情況惡化，本該同心協力的人起衝突。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如衝突本就無法避免，你只會在其中越陷越深。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城市將你浸染得黯淡了，涅梅絲。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以領袖——紅龍——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，愛布拉娜是不會為納斯爾紗帶來真正的生活的，對嗎，拉芙希妮？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說她做不到。她……其實並不喜歡說謊，除非另有制約……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她已經是整個塔拉的領袖，獨一無二的紅龍，還有什麼能制約她？！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲，你怎麼了？你看起來……不對勁……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。拉芙希妮殿下，我突然明白了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來那道火的確會侵染活人。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經依賴的人們，原來是一群中飽私囊的蛀蟲。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經信仰的領袖，原來是一條目無他人生死的惡龍。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經不惜性命捍衛的人們……我的摯友為他們而死。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，如果不是那條惡龍用紫火將他點燃，我都不知道他們還會對他做些什麼……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林問得對，等到夏末節過去，我該做什麼？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了復仇，我沒有什麼能做的了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_deathfire", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bgeffect", "name": "$eb_purple_fire", "slot": "bgover", "x": 20.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話說出口之後，拉芙希妮看見，最後一名還未沾染紫火的納斯爾紗居民，她身上燃起了火焰。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮殿下，您會因此將我當成城裡人的同類，愛布拉娜的僕臣嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，只是這致死的惡疾……終於傳染到了最後一個城裡人身上。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這樣，拉芙希妮殿下，我發誓，我會協助您把這支強加於您的舞一直跳下去，一直跳下去……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到那條邪惡的紅龍倒下。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我聽見了你的誓言。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我得離開納斯爾紗一趟。跟我一起走吧，涅梅絲。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守靈人的聚落，是嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。城裡已經沒有治癒那道火焰的希望，我得去找到任何可能幫得上忙的人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不會去。我已經沒有資格回去了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會在城市裡待下去。只要沒被紅龍注意到，沒被她撕成碎片……我會努力不讓事態繼續惡化。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這枚哨笛，就麻煩您還回去吧。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有……庫林也拜託您了。請您給庫林一個真正的葬禮。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮上需要親友念誦悼詞，我……我寫一份，您幫我唸，好嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g4_dragonsquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_writerub", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，給您。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我陪葦草一起離開。黑林現在不放任何人出入，我們兩個人，或許會順利一點。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，布莉吉，你得留下，我需要你的幫助。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一個人沒關係的。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也可以，但……涅梅絲，你越來越不像你自己了。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也許這就是復仇會把人變成的樣子吧。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read2"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}